influenza}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10303346\charrsid9714563  and since, which is a heart condition. But - a lady next d
oor who came in when mother died and of course there were six kids left with - and mother died very suddenly really in the night, and she said it was a miscarriage. Of course whether it was or not I don't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15934674 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10303346\charrsid9714563 Do you know if your mother had any other children in between the six of you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7025548 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10303346\charrsid9714563 Not that I know of - I've never hear of 'em, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15934674 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10303346\charrsid9714563 The lady next door thought it was a miscarriage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7025548 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10303346\charrsid9714563 She always said so.
