\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11556026\charrsid9714563 at school we had, you know, pli}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12918029\charrsid9714563 msoi}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10303346\charrsid9714563 l
 shoes to grumble about because it was somebody else's we used to wear, the teachers used to say, oh they'll fit you.
