as - oh, men never did did they. I mean that's what - like you see men shopping now with their wives don't you - wouldn't dream of doing that and - I know Saturdays mornings my brothers used to have to clean all our our shoes for Sunday and we used to hav
e to clean all the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11556026\charrsid9714563 spoons}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10303346\charrsid9714563  and forks and things like that. We had our set jobs, we weren't allowed to be lazy.
