cos my mother was always there in those days you see. She was up first - and she used to go to bed very late I remember but she said it was the only time she had any peace. My father used to go to bed and mother used to sit up I suppose - I don't know whe
ther she ever read or what but -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15934674 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10303346\charrsid9714563 Did he do any decorating or repairs?
