No, because the house as I said belonged to the railway and every three years they used to come right through and do every - every room. Which was very, very good.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15934674 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10303346\charrsid9714563 So your father didn't really have anything to do in the house?
