We couldn't - well, he could but he was very clumsy - he made a seat for the garden I remember once and he says, there, that'll - that'll be comfortable. And he stood it up and the thing wouldn'
t stand unless it leant on the fence - we always laughed about that. That's the sort of carpenter my father was. He was a good sport, you know, good father, very easy going and he used to consider when he give mother his money that was - that was that you
 see and he'd done his bit.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15934674 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10303346\charrsid9714563 He wasn't a handy man?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7025548 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10303346\charrsid9714563 Not a bit, no.
