My elder sister did, yes. But - she went into service when she was about - she'd be about fifteen I suppose. And she was there with an aunt of mine who was cook in this house until my mother died and t
hen I took her place and she came home and looked after the family. And she did that until she was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3897222 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10303346\charrsid9714563 .
