\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7025548 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10303346\charrsid9714563 Oh yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15934674 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10303346\charrsid9714563 Can you think of the sort of jobs that she had to do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7025548 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10303346\charrsid9714563 Well, anything really you know on Saturdays we were quite busy you know all doing all sorts of jobs.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15934674 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10303346\charrsid9714563 You had to wash up after lunch?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7025548 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10303346\charrsid9714563 Yes.
