\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15934674 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10303346\charrsid9714563 What about the boys, were they expected to do things?
