\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7025548 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10303346\charrsid9714563 Yes, it was expected always that, you know, you weren't human - you were expected to be on the run, you know what I mean. If there 
- she rang the bell wherever she was in the house you were expected almost to be there - before the bell stopped ringing, you know, that - of course it was a house that - all of them with stairs that you'd got to go upstairs. You weren't supposed to arriv
e out of breath eith}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2454274\charrsid9714563 er}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10303346\charrsid9714563 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15934674 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10303346\charrsid9714563 How did you know about this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7025548 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10303346\charrsid9714563 
Oh she'd tell you about breathing too hard and all that sort of thing. And she'd ring the bell sometimes and say - I'd go upstairs - say yes, madam, and wait. Oh I said, I could hit her sometim
es. And she'd say, tell Barker not to bang the iron down so hard. I can hear it up here. I'd go down and tell my aunt and my aunt'd - about twice as hard as she did before but I didn't blame her.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15934674 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10303346\charrsid9714563 Your aunt was there for a long time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7025548 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10303346\charrsid9714563 Altogether I think she was there about twenty-three years by the time she did lea
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15934674 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10303346\charrsid9714563 How did the housework go?
