My aunt had to cook you know and sort of - 'course in a very large house she wouldn't have been expected to do that but being a sort of just the two 
of us she used to do the dinning - oh she took tea in the morning to them at certain time. And - we used to get up at quarter past six and gave them - there were two stoves to do which my aunt did, light the kitchen stove and the dinning room o - whicheve
r room they were going to use. And then she used to do that and sweep the carpet which of course was a brush in those days. I used to dust it and lay the breakfast. Then they came down, the family, and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15934674 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10303346\charrsid9714563 What time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7025548 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10303346\charrsid9714563 Well - I think about nine. And I used to take the breakfast in. Then we had ours but you}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3421375\charrsid9714563  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10303346\charrsid9714563 
scarcely had time to eat. And - after that of course - I cleared breakfast away and - my aunt washed up. 'Cos I had to do the work upstairs you see, the - the hall to do and the front steps for abou
t - at Enfield there were about ten. Huge white steps - they had to be hearth}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3421375\charrsid9714563 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10303346\charrsid9714563 stoned.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15934674 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10303346\charrsid9714563 Every day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7025548 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10303346\charrsid9714563 
Every day. You couldn't reach them in one. You had to do it in two haves, you know, the - that was for eleven pound a year - the rise I had was two 
pounds. I had nine pounds a year at Stamford Hill. I said first of all I wouldn't go you see and she said, oh, we'll give you a rise if you'll come. And I went and I had eleven pounds - two pounds per year rise.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15934674 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10303346\charrsid9714563 What else did you have to do after you'd done the steps?
