ant me to do - you know, my main thing was to be kind and look after Joyce and that was all, you know, as long as she was happy that's all they expected of me you see. Well they were very, very kind like that. Used to go away for six weeks in the summer. 
I used to go with them and - used to go to pantomimes and children}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5272448\charrsid9714563 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10303346\charrsid9714563 
s parties and - all that sort of thing at Christmas you know. Used to go away for Christmas sometimes to her brother's. They had three children and a nurse and we used to have ever such good times.
