\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7025548 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10303346\charrsid9714563 Oh we had a bathroom, yes, yes.
