Yes. Not shopping, no. Well I might do shopping - I might sometimes say to the cook, do you want anything? But they didn't like me leaving the pram outside the shop. I did very little shopping actually. I used to look round shops for myself to buy - y
ou know, my clothes when I used to look - do window shopping. Used to walk to - Enfield, I've walked there. That's three and a half miles.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15934674 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10303346\charrsid9714563 With the pram?
