l. Some nice shops there. I used to sort of you know window shop for when I had my money to buy - anything I wanted.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15934674 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10303346\charrsid9714563 Were you allowed to talk to people while you were out?
