\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7025548 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10303346\charrsid9714563 No. No. I us
ed to go and see my aunt on a Sunday morning sometimes but she'd gone back - I told you she went back to Enfield. Well I knew the old lady - Mrs Figgis would be at church and I used to go and see - just there ever so quickly but of course I couldn't stay 
more than about twenty minutes because - I'd got to walk back. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15934674 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10303346\charrsid9714563 Did you ever go out with the family on a weekend or Bank Holiday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7025548 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10303346\charrsid9714563 No. We used to go away a lot but not weekends. He stayed at Eastbourne and -
