\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7025548 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10303346\charrsid9714563 Oh no, I had my fortnights holiday on my own. Used to come home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15934674 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10303346\charrsid9714563 That was their holiday I meant?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7025548 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10303346\charrsid9714563 Yes, used to go for about six weeks in the sommer to somewhere - Walton-on-}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9443724\charrsid9714563 
N}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10303346\charrsid9714563 aze or - had a cottage a Walton, right the other end of Walton, had a gate down to the beach, it was really very nice.
