\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15934674 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10303346\charrsid9714563 Did the cook?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7025548 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10303346\charrsid9714563 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15934674 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10303346\charrsid9714563 Only you and the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7025548 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10303346\charrsid9714563 The - yes, Joyce and Mr and Mrs Greenhill.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15934674 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10303346\charrsid9714563 And you just did normal things?
