\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7025548 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10303346\charrsid9714563 No, he'd been at the Times and - what are the other people that - can't think of the name now - }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
