\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15934674 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10303346\charrsid9714563 You didn't work after you marriage at all did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7025548 WR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10303346\charrsid9714563 No.
